headline: Bear of the Day: Lamb Weston (LW)
summary: Lamb Weston's top line has shown little growth over the past years, helping explain the consistently poor price action.

headline: Zoom Video and Lamb Weston have been highlighted as Zacks Bull and Bear of the Day
summary: Zoom Video rebounds on improving margins and cash flow, while Lamb Weston slumps after weak sales growth sends shares sharply lower.
